WEBVTT

00:01.402 --> 00:03.104
male announcer:
IN THE CRIMINAL JUSTICE SYSTEM,

00:03.137 --> 00:05.773
SEXUALLY BASED OFFENSES ARE
CONSIDERED ESPECIALLY HEINOUS.

00:05.806 --> 00:08.342
IN NEW YORK CITY,
THE DEDICATED DETECTIVES

00:08.376 --> 00:10.244
WHO INVESTIGATE
THESE VICIOUS FELONIES

00:10.278 --> 00:12.113
ARE MEMBERS OF AN ELITE SQUAD

00:12.146 --> 00:13.514
KNOWN AS
THE SPECIAL VICTIMS UNIT.

00:13.547 --> 00:15.549
THESE ARE THEIR STORIES.

00:18.286 --> 00:21.222
- 911.
WHAT'S YOUR EMERGENCY?

00:21.255 --> 00:23.191
HELLO?

00:23.224 --> 00:25.059
HELLO?
IS SOMEONE THERE?

00:25.093 --> 00:26.794
- HI.

00:26.827 --> 00:30.064
- 911.
IS EVERYTHING ALL RIGHT?

00:30.098 --> 00:32.166
CAN YOU TELL ME
YOUR NAME, HONEY?

00:32.200 --> 00:33.534
- SAM.

00:33.567 --> 00:35.569
- OKAY, SAM.
HOW OLD ARE YOU?

00:35.603 --> 00:37.271
- 3 1/2.

00:37.305 --> 00:40.474
- OKAY. AND, UH, CAN YOU
TELL ME WHAT'S WRONG, SAM?

00:40.508 --> 00:42.510
- MOMMY'S ASLEEP.

00:42.543 --> 00:45.613
EVEN IF I YELL LOUD,
SHE WON'T WAKE UP.

00:45.646 --> 00:47.281
- OKAY, ARE YOU
ALL BY YOURSELF?

00:47.315 --> 00:48.382
IS THERE ANYONE ELSE
IN THE HOUSE?

00:48.416 --> 00:51.419
- JUST ME.
MY BIG SISTER LEFT.

00:51.452 --> 00:52.420
- AND THE PHONE
YOU'RE CALLING ME FROM,

00:52.453 --> 00:54.822
DOES IT HAVE A CORD
THAT GOES INTO THE WALL?

00:54.855 --> 00:59.827
- IT HAS MY PICTURE.
I PLAY ANGRY BIRDS.

00:59.860 --> 01:01.562
- OKAY, SAM, I'M GONNA
SEND SOMEONE TO YOUR HOUSE.

01:01.595 --> 01:02.596
DO YOU KNOW YOUR ADDRESS?

01:02.630 --> 01:05.233
- YEAH.
NEW YORK, NEW YORK.

01:05.266 --> 01:07.335
MY BIG SISTER WAS MAD.

01:07.368 --> 01:09.837
- OKAY, SAM,
WE'RE GONNA HELP YOU, OKAY?

01:09.870 --> 01:12.873
JUST STAY ON THE PHONE.

01:12.906 --> 01:14.442
CAN YOU TELL ME ANYTHING
ABOUT WHERE YOU LIVE?

01:14.475 --> 01:15.609
IS THERE AN ELEVATOR?

01:15.643 --> 01:17.845
- YEAH. I PUSH FOUR.

01:17.878 --> 01:19.347
- OKAY, SAM, THAT'S GOOD.

01:19.380 --> 01:22.316
JUST SIT TIGHT.
DON'T HANG UP, OKAY?

01:22.350 --> 01:26.287
- OKAY.
I'LL SHOW YOU MY PICTURE.

01:26.320 --> 01:27.621
[knock on door]

01:27.655 --> 01:29.190
- SAM?

01:29.223 --> 01:31.325
- CATE?
YOU CAME BACK?

01:31.359 --> 01:33.194
- SAM, MY NAME IS OLIVIA.

01:33.227 --> 01:34.195
I'M WITH THE POLICE.

01:34.228 --> 01:36.364
- CAN YOU OPEN THE DOOR,
BUDDY?

01:36.397 --> 01:39.500
- SAM, WE WANT TO HELP
YOUR MOM.

01:40.568 --> 01:43.137
HEY.
- HEY, BUDDY.

01:43.171 --> 01:45.173
- YOU DID GREAT, SAM.

01:45.206 --> 01:46.207
- HEY, COULD YOU SHOW US
WHERE YOUR MOMMY IS?

01:46.240 --> 01:47.508
- OKAY.

01:52.346 --> 01:54.682
MOMMY, GET UP.
THE POLICE ARE HERE.

01:54.715 --> 01:56.317
- COME HERE, SWEETHEART.
COME HERE.

01:56.350 --> 01:58.386
- GET EMS IN HERE.

01:59.920 --> 02:02.190
- NOW, SAM, WE'RE GONNA
HELP YOUR MOM.

02:02.223 --> 02:03.624
SO CAN YOU TELL ME
WHAT HAPPENED?

02:03.657 --> 02:05.326
- I WAS SLEEPING.

02:05.359 --> 02:08.262
MY MOM AND MY SISTER
WERE FIGHTING

02:08.296 --> 02:12.600
ABOUT A--A BAD MAN
TAKING MY SISTER AWAY.

02:14.602 --> 02:16.470
- OKAY.

02:16.504 --> 02:19.240
SHE'S GONNA BE OKAY.

02:20.541 --> 02:23.511
[Law & Order theme]

02:23.544 --> 02:31.552
*

03:10.724 --> 03:13.661
- HI, LIV.

03:13.694 --> 03:15.696
I REACHED THE FATHER.
HE'S ON HIS WAY.

03:15.729 --> 03:16.730
- HOW'S THE MOTHER?

03:16.764 --> 03:18.232
- THEY'RE DOING AN MRI.

03:18.266 --> 03:19.967
SHE HAS A GASH
ON THE BACK OF HER HEAD.

03:20.000 --> 03:21.335
THE NEIGHBORS HEARD
SOME RAISED VOICES.

03:21.369 --> 03:23.437
NOTHING DRAMATIC.
WHAT DID THE KID SEE?

03:23.471 --> 03:25.606
- WELL, IT'S HARD TO TELL.
HE'S BARELY FOUR.

03:25.639 --> 03:28.276
HE SAID THAT HE HEARD
HIS MOTHER AND HIS SISTER

03:28.309 --> 03:30.411
FIGHTING ABOUT A BAD MAN.

03:30.444 --> 03:34.448
- HI, UH, I'M GEOFF AVERY,
UM, GRACE'S HUSBAND.

03:34.482 --> 03:35.383
WHERE'S MY WIFE?

03:35.416 --> 03:37.318
- MR. AVERY,
THEY'RE DOING A BRAIN SCAN.

03:37.351 --> 03:38.752
SHE SUSTAINED A HEAD INJURY.

03:38.786 --> 03:41.289
- OH, MY GOD.

03:41.322 --> 03:42.690
[kiss]

03:42.723 --> 03:45.526
SAM'S OKAY.

03:45.559 --> 03:47.328
WHERE'S CATE,
MY DAUGHTER?

03:47.361 --> 03:48.329
SHE WAS SUPPOSED TO BE
AT HOME.

03:48.362 --> 03:49.297
WHAT HAPPENED?

03:49.330 --> 03:51.499
- WE'RE TRYING TO
PIECE THAT TOGETHER NOW.

03:51.532 --> 03:54.435
NOW, HOW OLD IS YOUR DAUGHTER?
- 16.

03:54.468 --> 03:56.437
- CAN YOU GET IN TOUCH WITH HER?
- NO.

03:56.470 --> 03:58.472
SHE WAS TEXTING
AT THE BREAKFAST TABLE,

03:58.506 --> 03:59.673
SO I TOOK HER CELL PHONE
AWAY.

03:59.707 --> 04:02.710
- SO, GEOFF,
WHERE WERE YOU TONIGHT?

04:02.743 --> 04:05.346
- WITH MY SISTERS, CLEARING OUT
MY MOM'S APARTMENT.

04:05.379 --> 04:07.648
SHE PASSED AWAY LAST WEEK
FROM BREAST CANCER.

04:07.681 --> 04:09.483
LOOK, IF MY DAUGHTER'S
BEEN ABDUCTED,

04:09.517 --> 04:10.818
YOU NEED TO
PUT OUT AN AMBER ALERT.

04:10.851 --> 04:12.420
- WE CAN'T ISSUE
AN AMBER ALERT.

04:12.453 --> 04:14.522
NOBODY ACTUALLY SAW HER
BEING TAKEN.

04:14.555 --> 04:17.691
- MY WIFE'S UNCONSCIOUS,
MY DAUGHTER'S MISSING.

04:17.725 --> 04:19.026
- SHE MAY HAVE FALLEN.

04:19.059 --> 04:20.461
THERE WERE SIGNS THAT
SHE'D BEEN DRINKING.

04:20.494 --> 04:22.596
- DAMN IT.

04:22.630 --> 04:24.632
SHE SWORE TO ME
THAT WAS UNDER CONTROL.

04:24.665 --> 04:26.066
- RIGHT.

04:26.099 --> 04:27.668
SO DOES CATE
STAY OUT LATE?

04:27.701 --> 04:28.669
DOES SHE HAVE A BOYFRIEND?

04:28.702 --> 04:29.837
- I DON'T THINK SO.

04:29.870 --> 04:31.505
- BUT YOU DON'T KNOW?

04:31.539 --> 04:34.074
- SHE BLOCKED ME FROM
HER FACEBOOK PAGE LAST MONTH,

04:34.107 --> 04:35.309
ON HER BIRTHDAY.

04:35.343 --> 04:36.577
CHANGED HER PASSWORD.

04:36.610 --> 04:37.645
- WHAT ABOUT GIRLFRIENDS?

04:37.678 --> 04:40.047
COULD SHE BE OUT
WITH ANY OF THEM?

04:40.080 --> 04:42.383
- UH, ANGELA RIVA.

04:42.416 --> 04:45.419
THEY'VE BEEN BEST FRIENDS
SINCE KINDERGARTEN.

04:50.424 --> 04:51.459
- SO WHAT'S YOUR GUT?

04:51.492 --> 04:52.793
SHE'S OUT PARTYING,

04:52.826 --> 04:54.428
DOES THE WALK OF SHAME
IN THE MORNING?

04:54.462 --> 04:55.696
- WELL, NINE TIMES
OUT OF TEN,

04:55.729 --> 04:56.764
BUT I DON'T WANT TO
TAKE A CHANCE

04:56.797 --> 04:57.798
IF THIS IS A HOMICIDE.

04:57.831 --> 04:59.633
WE KEEP GOING.

05:01.802 --> 05:04.538
- CATE AND I HAVEN'T BEEN
FRIENDS SINCE FIFTH GRADE.

05:04.572 --> 05:06.440
- IS SHE IN SOME KIND
OF TROUBLE?

05:06.474 --> 05:07.641
- THAT DOESN'T SURPRISE YOU?

05:07.675 --> 05:08.709
- I WAS
HER SURROGATE MOTHER.

05:08.742 --> 05:09.710
SHE WAS HERE, EATING,
EVERY NIGHT.

05:09.743 --> 05:11.078
NEVER WANTED TO GO HOME.

05:11.111 --> 05:13.547
I TOLD ANGELA
TO STAY AWAY FROM HER.

05:13.581 --> 05:14.682
SHE HANGS WITH A BAD CROWD.

05:14.715 --> 05:16.450
- SHE'S BEEN
DIFFERENT LATELY, MOM.

05:16.484 --> 05:18.085
- DIFFERENT HOW?

05:18.118 --> 05:19.620
- LAST FEW WEEKS, I SAW HER
AT THE LIBRARY EVERY NIGHT,

05:19.653 --> 05:20.788
ON THE COMPUTER,

05:20.821 --> 05:23.424
REALLY TRYING TO
TURN HER GRADES AROUND.

05:23.457 --> 05:25.793
- YOU BUY THAT
STUDYING STORY?

05:25.826 --> 05:28.529
- MY GUESS IS, SHE DOESN'T
WANT HER PARENTS TO KNOW

05:28.562 --> 05:31.432
WHO SHE'S CHATTING WITH
ONLINE.

05:31.465 --> 05:32.533
- WHAT BOOKS
HAS SHE CHECKED OUT?

05:32.566 --> 05:33.567
THAT'S CONFIDENTIAL.

05:33.601 --> 05:35.536
- I UNDERSTAND THAT,
BUT THIS GIRL IS MISSING.

05:35.569 --> 05:36.837
- DO YOU HAVE A WARRANT?

05:36.870 --> 05:38.105
- I KNOW LIBRARIANS
CAN BE PRICKLY,

05:38.138 --> 05:39.306
BUT YOU'VE HEARD OF
THE PATRIOT ACT?

05:39.339 --> 05:42.376
- OH, NOW THIS MISSING GIRL
IS INVOLVED WITH TERRORISM?

05:42.410 --> 05:43.411
- IF WE HAVE TO,

05:43.444 --> 05:44.612
WE'LL GET THE FBI IN HERE
WITH A FISA WARRANT.

05:44.645 --> 05:45.813
THEY'VE NEVER BEEN
TURNED DOWN.

05:45.846 --> 05:47.448
- AND THAT'LL TAKE
HALF A DAY,

05:47.481 --> 05:48.849
AND THE CLOCK'S TICKING
ON THIS GIRL.

05:48.882 --> 05:51.485
- OKAY, FINE.

05:51.519 --> 05:52.853
I JUST WISH YOU GUYS
WOULD GIVE MORE THOUGHT

05:52.886 --> 05:54.154
TO CIVIL LIBERTIES.

05:54.187 --> 05:57.658
- WE DO. EVERY DAY.
NOW JUST, PLEASE, HUNT.

05:57.691 --> 05:59.693
[typing]

05:59.727 --> 06:01.595
- HERE'S YOUR "TERROR CELL."

06:01.629 --> 06:02.796
IN THE PAST MONTH,

06:02.830 --> 06:04.765
CATE HAS CHECKED OUT
THE HUNGER GAMES TRILOGY

06:04.798 --> 06:08.569
AND TWO BOOKS ON CHILDREN
BORN THROUGH SPERM DONATION.

06:08.602 --> 06:11.439
- "HEARTWARMING STORIES
FROM DONOR CHILDREN

06:11.472 --> 06:13.474
"WHO CONNECTED
WITH BIOLOGICAL PARENTS,

06:13.507 --> 06:14.508
BROTHERS, AND SISTERS."

06:14.542 --> 06:16.744
- WHICH COMPUTER
DID SHE USE?

06:16.777 --> 06:19.647
- CATE AVERY'S BEEN MISSING
FOR 15 HOURS.

06:19.680 --> 06:20.948
WAS SHE ABDUCTED?
DID SHE RUN AWAY?

06:20.981 --> 06:22.550
- UNTIL THE MOTHER CAN TALK,
WE CAN'T BE SURE.

06:22.583 --> 06:24.452
- THERE'S NO HITS
ON HER ATM,

06:24.485 --> 06:25.919
NO NEW CONTACTS
IN HER CELL PHONE.

06:25.953 --> 06:27.755
- YOU GUYS,
LOOK WHO WE FOUND

06:27.788 --> 06:28.889
WANDERING THROUGH
THE HALLWAY.

06:28.922 --> 06:29.923
- HEY.

06:29.957 --> 06:32.426
- JOHN, HEY.
GLAD TO GET YOUR CALL.

06:32.460 --> 06:33.927
- HEY.
- UHH!

06:33.961 --> 06:35.463
- THE DOCTOR WAS IN TOWN
AT A CONVENTION,

06:35.496 --> 06:36.329
DROPPED THE DIME.

06:36.363 --> 06:37.498
THOUGHT HE COULD HELP US
WITH THE CASE.

06:37.531 --> 06:39.667
YOU ALREADY KNOW AMANDA.
THIS IS DETECTIVE NICK AMARO.

06:39.700 --> 06:40.668
- HOW ARE YOU?

06:40.701 --> 06:41.835
- HOW'S THE NEW ASSIGNMENT?

06:41.869 --> 06:43.837
- A SINGLE, GAY
CHINESE-AMERICAN MAN,

06:43.871 --> 06:46.774
LIVING IN OKLAHOMA CITY,
OPPOSED TO THE DEATH PENALTY.

06:46.807 --> 06:47.875
IT'S HEAVEN.
- [laughs]

06:47.908 --> 06:49.176
- WHAT DO YOU GOT?

06:49.209 --> 06:50.511
- WELL, WHAT DO YOU KNOW

06:50.544 --> 06:52.580
ABOUT THE PSYCHOLOGY
OF DONOR CHILDREN?

06:52.613 --> 06:53.714
- THAT IS A BIG TOPIC.

06:53.747 --> 06:56.517
SPERM BANKS HAVE ALWAYS
PROTECTED DONOR CONFIDENTIALITY,

06:56.550 --> 06:57.785
BUT UNTIL RECENTLY,

06:57.818 --> 06:59.987
NOBODY THOUGHT ABOUT HOW
THAT AFFECTS OFFSPRING.

07:00.020 --> 07:01.655
- 'CAUSE WE'VE GOT
A MISSING TEENAGE GIRL

07:01.689 --> 07:02.590
RESEARCHING ALL OF THIS

07:02.623 --> 07:04.892
WHO JUST JOINED
MEETYOURDONORSIBLING.COM.

07:04.925 --> 07:06.494
- I'VE SEEN THOSE SITES.

07:06.527 --> 07:07.661
TURKEY-BASTER KIDS
LOOKING TO SEE

07:07.695 --> 07:08.862
IF THEY HAVE
HALF BROTHERS AND SISTERS.

07:08.896 --> 07:11.799
- I THINK THE PREFERRED TERM
IS ARTIFICIAL INSEMINATION.

07:11.832 --> 07:13.567
- ISN'T THAT WHAT I SAID?

07:13.601 --> 07:14.602
- EITHER WAY,
IT'S NOT UNCOMMON

07:14.635 --> 07:16.537
FOR THESE CHILDREN TO TRY
AND FIND THEIR DONORS.

07:16.570 --> 07:18.672
- YOU KNOW, MAYBE THAT'S WHAT
THE RAISED VOICES WERE ABOUT.

07:18.706 --> 07:21.008
OUR GIRL MAY HAVE GOTTEN
INTO A FIGHT WITH HER MOTHER

07:21.041 --> 07:22.576
BEFORE SHE DISAPPEARED.

07:22.610 --> 07:23.811
- A GIRL SEARCHING
FOR HER ROOTS.

07:23.844 --> 07:24.912
THAT COULD CAUSE
SOME TENSION.

07:24.945 --> 07:26.580
- WELL, THE MOTHER
CAN TELL US.

07:26.614 --> 07:28.949
GRACE AVERY'S BEEN RELEASED
FROM THE HOSPITAL.

07:31.284 --> 07:34.788
- I SLIPPED, HIT MY HEAD,
WOKE UP IN THE HOSPITAL.

07:34.822 --> 07:36.657
GEOFF SAYS CATE'S MISSING.

07:36.690 --> 07:38.692
- SAM SAID THAT YOU
AND CATE WERE FIGHTING

07:38.726 --> 07:39.993
ABOUT A "BAD MAN."

07:40.027 --> 07:41.228
- NO.

07:41.261 --> 07:42.630
- DO YOU KNOW
WHAT HE MEANT BY THAT?

07:42.663 --> 07:44.698
- HE'S GOT AN IMAGINATION.

07:44.732 --> 07:45.833
I-I-I DON'T KNOW.

07:45.866 --> 07:48.669
- WHAT WERE YOU AND CATE
FIGHTING ABOUT?

07:48.702 --> 07:51.839
- JUST MOTHER-DAUGHTER STUFF.

07:51.872 --> 07:54.675
- WE KNOW THAT CATE
WAS SEARCHING ONLINE

07:54.708 --> 07:55.843
FOR DONOR RELATIVES,

07:55.876 --> 07:58.612
AND I'M GUESSING
THAT YOU DO TOO.

07:58.646 --> 08:03.517
- [sighs]

08:03.551 --> 08:09.657
MY HUSBAND CAN NEVER KNOW.
PLEASE.

08:09.690 --> 08:10.991
- OKAY.

08:11.024 --> 08:15.996
- CATE WAS CONCEIVED
WITH DONOR SPERM.

08:16.029 --> 08:19.733
SOMEHOW SHE TRACKED DOWN
THE DONOR ONLINE

08:19.767 --> 08:21.268
AND WAS ABOUT TO MEET HIM.

08:21.301 --> 08:23.937
I SAID NO.
WE FOUGHT.

08:23.971 --> 08:26.707
THAT'S WHAT SAM
MUST HAVE HEARD.

08:26.740 --> 08:30.678
- AND GEOFF BELIEVES HE'S
CATE'S BIOLOGICAL FATHER?

08:30.711 --> 08:32.580
- YEAH.

08:32.613 --> 08:34.281
- SO YOU WENT
TO A SPERM BANK.

08:34.314 --> 08:37.918
- I GOT PREGNANT WITH CATE.

08:37.951 --> 08:40.621
GEOFF AND I GOT MARRIED.

08:40.654 --> 08:42.289
AND THEN,
12 YEARS LATER,

08:42.322 --> 08:46.627
I USED THE SAME SAMPLE
TO HAVE SAM.

08:46.660 --> 08:48.562
- HOW DID CATE FIND OUT?

08:48.596 --> 08:53.734
- SHE WAS MAKING A MEMORY BOOK
FOR HER GRANDMOTHER.

08:53.767 --> 08:55.836
UH, GOING THROUGH
OLD PHOTO BOXES,

08:55.869 --> 09:01.642
SHE FOUND A MEDICAL CARD
FOR NEW YORK CRYOGENICS.

09:01.675 --> 09:03.844
"DONOR 141."

09:06.780 --> 09:09.316
- GEOFF NEVER KNEW
ABOUT ANY OF THIS?

09:09.349 --> 09:10.584
- FAMILY SECRETS.

09:10.618 --> 09:12.052
- LIV,
THIS IS BEYOND THAT.

09:12.085 --> 09:15.055
HIS WIFE LIED TO HIM ABOUT
THEIR TWO KIDS FOR 16 YEARS.

09:15.088 --> 09:16.790
SHE MANIPULATED HIM
INTO MARRYING HER.

09:16.824 --> 09:19.760
- HOLD ON, NICK. WE'VE GOT
A HIT ON CATE'S DEBIT CARD.

09:19.793 --> 09:23.597
COFFEE BAR AT LINCOLN CENTER.
$24.

09:23.631 --> 09:24.798
FIN AND ROLLINS ARE EN ROUTE.

09:24.832 --> 09:27.935
- 24 BUCKS.
THAT'S A LOT OF LATTE.

09:27.968 --> 09:29.970
- MAYBE CATE'S NOT ALONE.

09:30.971 --> 09:36.076
- * MY ONE AND ONLY LOVE

09:36.109 --> 09:40.614
[soft jazz music
continues in headphones]

09:45.385 --> 09:46.386
- HI.

09:46.419 --> 09:49.690
- CATE AVERY?

09:49.723 --> 09:50.891
- WHO ARE YOU GUYS?

09:50.924 --> 09:51.925
- WE'RE THE POLICE.

09:51.959 --> 09:56.029
YOUR MOTHER'S
LOOKING FOR YOU.

09:56.063 --> 09:58.065
- ARE YOU EXPECTING SOMEONE,
SWEETIE?

10:06.406 --> 10:07.875
- MY LITTLE BROTHER WATCHES
TOO MUCH CYBERCHASE.

10:07.908 --> 10:09.109
I WASN'T KIDNAPPED,
ALL RIGHT?

10:09.142 --> 10:12.045
- OH, WE KNOW, CATE,
BUT WE ALSO KNOW

10:12.079 --> 10:13.747
THAT YOU WERE SEARCHING
ON THE INTERNET

10:13.781 --> 10:15.115
FOR YOUR BIOLOGICAL FATHER.

10:15.148 --> 10:17.117
IS THAT WHO YOU MET
LAST NIGHT?

10:17.150 --> 10:18.852
- I DON'T KNOW WHAT
YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

10:18.886 --> 10:19.887
I WAS WITH A GIRLFRIEND.

10:19.920 --> 10:23.123
- HMM. WELL, WE'RE GONNA
NEED HER NAME, HONEY.

10:23.156 --> 10:25.092
- WHY AM I EVEN HERE?
I DIDN'T DO ANYTHING WRONG.

10:25.125 --> 10:27.995
- FOR STARTERS, YOU DIDN'T
COME HOME LAST NIGHT,

10:28.028 --> 10:31.999
AND YOU LEFT YOUR THREE-YEAR-OLD
BROTHER HOME ALONE

10:32.032 --> 10:33.767
AND YOUR MOTHER
UNCONSCIOUS ON THE FLOOR.

10:33.801 --> 10:34.968
- THAT WAS HER FAULT.

10:35.002 --> 10:37.104
SHE WAS DRINKING.
SHE FELL.

10:37.137 --> 10:39.907
THEY DON'T CARE ABOUT ME,
I DON'T CARE ABOUT THEM.

10:39.940 --> 10:41.074
- WHY DO YOU THINK
THEY DON'T CARE ABOUT YOU?

10:41.108 --> 10:43.143
BECAUSE THEY NEVER TOLD YOU
WHO YOUR REAL FATHER WAS?

10:43.176 --> 10:46.213
- THEY LIED TO ME.
MY WHOLE LIFE.

10:46.246 --> 10:48.816
- AND YOU FOUND OUT
THE TRUTH ON YOUR OWN.

10:48.849 --> 10:50.718
YOU'RE A GOOD DETECTIVE.

10:50.751 --> 10:52.185
- BUT SO ARE WE.

10:52.219 --> 10:54.121
YOU'RE 16.

10:54.154 --> 10:55.455
YOU STAYED OUT ALL NIGHT

10:55.488 --> 10:57.691
WITH A MAN THAT YOU MET
ON THE INTERNET.

10:57.725 --> 11:00.060
WE'RE GONNA FIND HIM.

11:01.261 --> 11:03.096
- MR. AVERY'S HERE
TO TAKE CATE HOME.

11:03.130 --> 11:04.998
- THANK GOD YOU'RE ALL RIGHT.

11:05.032 --> 11:08.035
- HERE TO CLEAN UP
ANOTHER MESS, DAD?

11:10.470 --> 11:12.773
- MAKE YOU WISH
YOU HAD A DAUGHTER?

11:12.806 --> 11:15.108
- SHE CLAIMS SHE WAS HAVING
COFFEE WITH A GIRLFRIEND.

11:15.142 --> 11:17.177
- LOOK, THIS SON OF A BITCH
MIGHT BE A PRO.

11:17.210 --> 11:19.179
I MEAN, LOOK HOW HE SITS
WITH HIS BACK TO THE CAMERA.

11:19.212 --> 11:21.214
I MEAN, LOOK AT THIS.

11:23.216 --> 11:26.086
AS SOON AS HE SEES
