- THAT'S WHAT I TRIED
TO TELL HER.

13:21.902 --> 13:23.270
- WELL, SHE SAID
THAT IT WAS DONOR--

13:23.303 --> 13:26.073
- IT'S DONOR 141.
- SO COULD YOU JUST CHECK?

13:26.106 --> 13:27.240
- YES, OF COURSE.

13:27.274 --> 13:29.176
- THERE'S NO HARM IN CHECKING.

13:29.209 --> 13:30.310
- THAT'S RIGHT.
OKAY.

13:30.343 --> 13:32.179
- YEAH. I'M SORRY.

13:32.212 --> 13:35.348
WE ACTUALLY RAN OUT OF DONOR 141
ABOUT FIVE YEARS AGO.

13:35.382 --> 13:36.950
HE WAS VERY POPULAR.

13:36.984 --> 13:37.985
- YOU KNOW WHAT?

13:38.018 --> 13:40.253
COULD YOU JUST SHOW US
HIS PROFILE?

13:40.287 --> 13:43.190
AND THEN MAYBE
WE CAN FIND SOMEONE

13:43.223 --> 13:46.626
WHOSE PROFILE
IS CLOSE TO HIS.

13:46.659 --> 13:49.329
- ALL RIGHT, WHY NOT?
JUST GIVE ME A SECOND.

13:49.362 --> 13:52.165
