- YES.

13:55.302 --> 13:57.237
- OF COURSE I KNEW
THEY WERE MEETING.

13:57.270 --> 13:59.406
ASHLEY WAS ALWAYS
SO CURIOUS ABOUT HIM.

13:59.439 --> 14:01.975
- YEAH, I GOT IN CONTACT
WITH HIM THROUGH THE WEBSITE.

14:02.009 --> 14:05.278
- SO, HOW DID YOU
AND YOUR DONOR FATHER

14:05.312 --> 14:06.313
ARRANGE TO MEET?

14:06.346 --> 14:08.081
- OH, WE'D BEEN EMAILING

14:08.115 --> 14:10.617
ABOUT ME COMING TO NEW YORK
OR HIM COMING TO BALTIMORE,

14:10.650 --> 14:11.418
AND THEN
MY SCHOOL THEATRE GROUP

14:11.451 --> 14:12.953
