TO THE CITY LAST YEAR.

14:12.986 --> 14:14.421
MEMORIAL DAY WEEKEND.

14:14.454 --> 14:16.023
- SO WHAT CAN YOU
TELL US ABOUT HIM?

14:16.056 --> 14:20.527
- UM, DR. BAKER,
HE'S--HE'S AMAZING.

14:20.560 --> 14:22.529
BUT HE HAS A FAMILY
OF HIS OWN,

14:22.562 --> 14:24.364
