ABOUT ME.

14:24.397 --> 14:27.400
- SO WHAT DID YOU
AND DR. BAKER TALK ABOUT?

14:27.434 --> 14:29.937
- UM, HE TOLD ME
ABOUT HIS WORK.

14:29.970 --> 14:31.671
HE'S ONE OF THE BEST DOCTORS
IN NEW YORK.

14:31.704 --> 14:34.041
EX-VIVO LUNG TRANSPLANTS.

14:34.074 --> 14:34.841
SAVES LIVES.

14:34.874 --> 14:37.911
