14:41.949 --> 14:43.984
IT WAS IN BETWEEN SHOWS.

14:44.017 --> 14:45.685
THEN I WENT WITH MY CLASS
TO SEE, UM,

14:45.718 --> 14:47.988
PHANTOM OF THE OPERA.

14:48.021 --> 14:49.689
- SHE BROUGHT ME
A SIGNED PLAYBILL.

14:49.722 --> 14:51.258
- YEAH.
[laughs]

14:51.291 --> 14:52.659
