15:42.609 --> 15:43.977
- YEAH, JUST ABOUT.

15:44.011 --> 15:45.645
AW, BUDDY.

15:45.678 --> 15:47.981
- GOT A LITTLE...
RUNNY NOSE.

15:48.015 --> 15:49.682
THERE YOU GO, PAL.

15:49.716 --> 15:53.053
- I'M GONNA TAKE HIM BACK
TO GET CHANGED.

15:53.086 --> 15:54.654
- OH. I SHOULD GO
HELP ASHLEY--

15:54.687 --> 15:56.323
- OF COURSE.
- WITH THE BABY.

15:56.356 --> 15:58.058
- SURE.

16:00.760 --> 16:03.596
