THE DONOR DAD.

16:06.499 --> 16:07.634
AND DO THE MATH.

16:07.667 --> 16:10.370
THE BABY WAS BORN
NINE MONTHS LATER.

16:10.403 --> 16:12.739
MAYBE SHY JOEY
ISN'T THE FATHER.

16:12.772 --> 16:15.742
- WELL,
THIS SHOULD TELL US.

16:15.775 --> 16:17.444
- SO WE'RE SAYING
A DONOR FATHER

16:17.477 --> 16:20.647
HAD A CHILD WITH
HIS BIOLOGICAL DAUGHTER?

16:20.680 --> 16:22.482
- THEY'RE TESTING
THE BABY'S DNA NOW.

16:22.515 --> 16:23.750
I HOPE I'M WRONG.

16:23.783 --> 16:25.618
- WHAT KIND OF PREDATOR
ARE WE LOOKING AT?

16:25.652 --> 16:28.155
- WELL, IT COULD BE A PREDATOR,
OR IT COULD BE GSA.

16:28.188 --> 16:29.756
GENETIC SEXUAL ATTRACTION.

16:29.789 --> 16:32.359
WHEN CHILDREN
ARE SEPARATED EARLY

16:32.392 --> 16:33.626
FROM THEIR
BIOLOGICAL RELATIVES

16:33.660 --> 16:35.528
AND THEN REUNITED
MANY YEARS LATER,

16:35.562 --> 16:37.597
SOMETIMES THERE ARE
OVERWHELMING FEELINGS

16:37.630 --> 16:38.598
OF SEXUAL ATTRACTION.

16:38.631 --> 16:40.133
THIS CAN HAPPEN
BETWEEN SIBLINGS

16:40.167 --> 16:42.102
OR BETWEEN
A FATHER AND DAUGHTER.

16:42.135 --> 16:43.770
- DO WE HAVE ANYTHING
FROM THE DONOR PROFILE?

16:43.803 --> 16:47.507
- WE DO. UH, HE IS 6'1",
BROWN HAIR, BLUE EYES.

16:47.540 --> 16:50.177
CORNELL UNDERGRAD,
'93, PRE-MED.

16:50.210 --> 16:52.112
- AND HE TOLD ASHLEY
HE WAS A DOCTOR.

16:52.145 --> 16:54.047
THE NAME HE USED
WAS CALVIN BAKER.

16:54.081 --> 16:58.118
- THEY SAID HE WAS AN EX-VIVO
LUNG TRANSPLANT SPECIALIST.

16:58.151 --> 16:59.719
