AS OF LAST MEMORIAL DAY.

16:59.752 --> 17:01.421
- WELL, THERE'S NOTHING
FOR THAT NAME,

17:01.454 --> 17:05.525
BUT EX-VIVO DOCS, CORNELL,
THAT'S GOTTA BE A SMALL POOL.

17:05.558 --> 17:07.060
