CLASS OF 1993.

17:10.230 --> 17:13.600
- HERE WE GO.
"SURGEON AT GROLLIER LEMAY.

17:13.633 --> 17:15.802
EX-VIVO LUNG TRANSPLANT
SPECIALIST."

17:15.835 --> 17:19.406
