17:35.222 --> 17:36.689
- "CLOSE TO GOD."

17:36.723 --> 17:38.158
THE SAME WORDS
HE USED WITH ASHLEY.

17:38.191 --> 17:39.659
- YEAH, WELL,

17:39.692 --> 17:43.130
