THIS DOCTOR A HOUSE CALL.

17:46.266 --> 17:47.867
- DR. BARNES.

17:47.900 --> 17:50.170
- EXCUSE ME.

17:50.203 --> 17:51.838
CAN I HELP YOU?

17:51.871 --> 17:53.673
- UM, THESE ARE DETECTIVES.

17:53.706 --> 17:55.442
- WHAT'S THIS ABOUT?

17:55.475 --> 17:59.446
- UH, WE SHOULD TALK
PRIVATELY.

