18:34.247 --> 18:35.582
IS SOMEBODY TRYING
TO CONTACT ME?

18:35.615 --> 18:37.617
BECAUSE I DONATED
ON THE CONDITION OF ANONYMITY.

18:37.650 --> 18:39.719
- SO YOU'VE NEVER CONTACTED
ANY OF YOUR OFFSPRING?

18:39.752 --> 18:43.490
- NO. AND I HAVEN'T EVEN
TOLD MY WIFE THAT I WAS A DONOR.

18:43.523 --> 18:45.225
AND IF SOMEBODY'S
TRYING TO FIND ME,

18:45.258 --> 18:47.594
UNDER NO CIRCUMSTANCES
WOULD I AGREE TO THAT.

18:47.627 --> 18:49.929
- SO WHERE WERE YOU
THURSDAY NIGHT?

