19:12.885 --> 19:14.687
THAT YOU WERE
AN EX-VIVO LUNG SURGEON

19:14.721 --> 19:17.524
AND HOW HOLDING A LIFE
IN YOUR HAND

19:17.557 --> 19:18.658
MAKES YOU FEEL CLOSE TO GOD.

19:18.691 --> 19:20.560
