- ARE YOU SURE, MELISSA?

20:17.884 --> 20:19.619
- I'M SURE.

20:21.321 --> 20:22.989
- NO.

20:23.022 --> 20:24.791
- CATE, WE NEED YOU
TO BE CERTAIN.

20:24.824 --> 20:25.992
- I'M TELLING YOU,

20:26.025 --> 20:27.694
I'VE NEVER SEEN ANY
OF THESE GUYS BEFORE.

20:27.727 --> 20:29.028
- WE'RE DONE HERE,
DETECTIVES.

20:29.061 --> 20:30.597
THREE FOR THREE.

20:30.630 --> 20:32.632
