20:35.668 --> 20:38.004
- RIGHT HEIGHT, BUILD.
IT COULD BE BARNES.

20:38.037 --> 20:40.707
- WELL, HIS WIFE ALIBIS HIM
FOR THAT NIGHT,

20:40.740 --> 20:42.675
BUT WIVES LIE.

20:42.709 --> 20:45.345
- NONE OF THESE OTHER GIRLS
IDed COLIN BARNES?

20:45.378 --> 20:46.813
ARE THEY ALL PROTECTING HIM?

20:46.846 --> 20:48.415
- IF THEY HAD SEX WITH HIM,
THEY MIGHT BE.

20:48.448 --> 20:51.318
- BUSY GUY, SUCCESSFUL SURGEON,
FAMILY MAN.

20:51.351 --> 20:53.853
