SEDUCE HIS DONOR DAUGHTERS?

20:53.886 --> 20:55.788
- WELL, HE DOES HAVE
A GOD COMPLEX.

20:55.822 --> 20:57.757
- WE'RE TRACKING
THE HOTEL ROOM CHARGES.

20:57.790 --> 20:59.359
