IN EACH OTHER'S HEARTS.

23:48.227 --> 23:51.998
- HE TOLD ME HE WANTED
ONE THING IN LIFE--

23:52.031 --> 23:54.501
TO GIVE ME AWAY
AT MY WEDDING.

23:54.534 --> 23:57.169
TO WALK ME DOWN THE AISLE.

23:57.203 --> 23:59.205
