32:38.190 --> 32:41.093
IS THAT RIGHT, ANNE?

32:41.127 --> 32:43.062
- HE COULD BE UNDER
THE IMPRESSION

32:43.095 --> 32:45.497
THAT COLIN STOLE ME AWAY.

32:45.531 --> 32:48.367
AFTER I BROKE IT OFF WITH SEAN,
COLIN ASKED ME OUT.

32:48.400 --> 32:49.968
- YOU KNOW ANYTHING
ABOUT THIS?

32:52.404 --> 32:55.041
- YEAH, THAT'S RIGHT.
NOW I REMEMBER.

32:55.074 --> 32:57.476
