- RIGHT. SHE CONTACTED YOU.
- YES.

34:04.743 --> 34:06.578
SHE OBVIOUSLY NEEDS ME
RIGHT NOW.

34:06.612 --> 34:08.114
- YOU TWO ARE CLOSE.

34:08.147 --> 34:10.516
- WE SHARED A CONNECTION
FROM THE MOMENT WE MET.

34:10.549 --> 34:11.683
- AT PHILIP'S PARTY.

34:11.717 --> 34:14.586
SHE WAS WHAT, 15?

34:14.620 --> 34:17.189
SHE'S A LOVELY GIRL.

34:17.223 --> 34:19.158
- BEAUTIFUL.
- YEAH.

34:19.191 --> 34:21.260
- SPECIAL.

34:21.293 --> 34:22.561
YOU KNOW,
FOR A FEW SECONDS,

34:22.594 --> 34:24.196
I COULD HAVE SWORN
I WAS LOOKING AT ANNE.

34:24.230 --> 34:26.598
- SO YOU STRUCK UP
A CONVERSATION,

34:26.632 --> 34:28.600
TOLD HER YOU KNEW
HER PARENTS.

34:28.634 --> 34:30.702
- WELL, SHE WAS JUST HAPPY TO
HAVE SOMEONE TO TALK TO.

34:30.736 --> 34:34.706
COLIN WAS BUSY PONTIFICATING,
ANNE WAS PREGNANT, DISTRACTED.

34:34.740 --> 34:36.775
- HAVEN'T WE SEEN ENOUGH
OF THIS CHARADE?

34:36.808 --> 34:38.577
- THE DETECTIVES KNOW
WHAT THEY'RE DOING.

34:38.610 --> 34:42.114
EMPATHY, PROJECTION.
THEY'RE GETTING HIM TO TALK.

34:42.148 --> 34:45.217
- ALL TAYLOR NEEDED WAS SOMEONE
TO LISTEN TO HER, TO SEE HER.

34:45.251 --> 34:46.685
NOT LIKE HER FATHER,

34:46.718 --> 34:48.520
WHO WANTS HER ON THE SHELF
LIKE SOME IVY LEAGUE TROPHY.

34:48.554 --> 34:50.589
- SO YOU GAVE HER
THE ATTENTION.

34:50.622 --> 34:54.793
LIKE THE ATTENTION THAT YOU GAVE
TO COLIN'S OTHER DAUGHTERS.

34:54.826 --> 34:56.695
HIS DONOR DAUGHTERS.

35:07.273 --> 35:10.276
- I KNEW HE HAD
DONATED SPERM IN COLLEGE.

35:11.810 --> 35:14.880
AFTER TALKING TO TAYLOR AND
SEEING HOW LONELY SHE WAS,

35:14.913 --> 35:16.815
I STARTED WONDERING
ABOUT HIS OTHER DAUGHTERS.

35:16.848 --> 35:23.255
- WELL, IT'S NOT AS IF HE CARED
ABOUT ANY OF THEM, RIGHT?

35:23.289 --> 35:25.824
- THAT GUY...

35:25.857 --> 35:27.926
BEATING
THE BISHOP FOR A LIVING,

35:27.959 --> 35:30.529
PLAYING GOD.

35:30.562 --> 35:31.530
HE'S GOT A HUNDRED KIDS
OUT THERE.

35:31.563 --> 35:34.200
HE NEVER THOUGHT
FOR ONE SECOND WHAT IT MEANT

35:34.233 --> 35:36.535
FOR THEM TO GROW UP
WITH A HOLE IN THEIR LIVES.

35:36.568 --> 35:38.770
IN PAIN.
FATHERLESS.

35:38.804 --> 35:41.273
- SO YOU BECAME THAT FATHER.

35:41.307 --> 35:43.942
YOU WENT ONLINE
TO THE DONOR WEBSITE,

35:43.975 --> 35:47.646
YOU POSED AS DONOR 141,
ARRANGED TO MEET THE GIRLS.

35:47.679 --> 35:50.716
- I JUST WANTED TO GIVE THEM
A FATHER'S LOVE.

35:50.749 --> 35:52.318
- SURE.

35:55.354 --> 35:57.856
- THE EMOTIONS
WERE SO STRONG.

35:57.889 --> 36:00.259
THEY NEEDED MORE...

36:03.629 --> 36:06.398
SO I GAVE THEM
WHAT THEY NEEDED.

36:07.633 --> 36:10.702
I WAS A BETTER FATHER
THAN HE EVER WAS.

36:10.736 --> 36:13.305
HE DOESN'T DESERVE DAUGHTERS.

36:13.339 --> 36:15.407
HE DOESN'T DESERVE
A FAMILY.

36:21.980 --> 36:24.350
THEY'RE OUT THERE,
AREN'T THEY?

36:31.923 --> 36:33.659
I KNOW ANNE'S HERE.

36:35.627 --> 36:37.896
- SHE'S RIGHT OUTSIDE,
SEAN.

36:40.632 --> 36:42.901
SO TALK TO HER.

36:44.035 --> 36:46.405
- HE DOESN'T DESERVE YOU,
ANNE.

36:56.982 --> 37:02.288
I WILL NEVER FORGET SEEING YOU
AT THAT PARTY,

37:02.321 --> 37:05.324
PREGNANT, GLOWING.

37:05.357 --> 37:07.926
YOU SMILED RIGHT AT ME.

37:07.959 --> 37:10.662
YOU SAID,
"WE'RE SO BLESSED.

37:10.696 --> 37:11.897
THIS IS OUR MIRACLE BABY."

37:11.930 --> 37:12.898
[bangs metal]

37:12.931 --> 37:14.333
[exhales]

37:14.366 --> 37:16.668
WELL, NO MIRACLES FOR ME.

37:16.702 --> 37:18.970
I NEVER FOUND
THE RIGHT ONE.

37:22.474 --> 37:24.476
UNTIL NOW.

37:25.944 --> 37:27.679
TILL TAYLOR.

37:29.448 --> 37:32.818
- TELL HER
WHERE HER DAUGHTER IS.

37:32.851 --> 37:37.055
- I'LL TELL YOU, ANNE.
ONLY YOU.

37:37.088 --> 37:39.358
BUT I NEED TO SEE YOU
FIRST.

37:46.932 --> 37:48.934
- HERE WE GO.

37:48.967 --> 37:51.403
- WHERE'S MY DAUGHTER?

37:51.437 --> 37:52.270
PLEASE.

37:52.304 --> 37:54.906
- CAN'T WE JUST TALK
LIKE WE USED TO?

37:54.940 --> 37:59.445
- I'VE HURT YOU, SEAN.
I KNOW THAT.

37:59.478 --> 38:03.449
AND I WANT YOU
TO KNOW THAT I'M SORRY.

38:03.482 --> 38:08.754
- I'M GONNA ASK YOU
FOR ONE SIMPLE FAVOR.

38:08.787 --> 38:10.856
- AND IF I GIVE IT
TO YOU,

38:10.889 --> 38:12.424
WILL YOU TELL ME
WHERE TAYLOR IS?

38:23.435 --> 38:25.504
- ONE DANCE.

38:27.506 --> 38:31.443
WE NEVER GOT TO DANCE.

38:31.477 --> 38:33.779
YOU ALWAYS SAID,
"NEXT TIME."

38:33.812 --> 38:35.514
"NEXT TIME."

38:38.884 --> 38:41.387
HOW ABOUT NOW?

38:44.390 --> 38:47.726
- WHATEVER YOU WANT,
SEAN.

38:47.759 --> 38:50.462
- AND I WANT HIM TO WATCH.

38:51.797 --> 38:54.933
YOUR HUSBAND, THE DOCTOR.

38:54.966 --> 38:57.969
I WANT HIM TO FEEL
WHAT IT'S LIKE

38:58.003 --> 39:00.105
TO SEE YOU
WITH ANOTHER MAN.

39:02.774 --> 39:05.744
[My One And Only playing]

39:05.777 --> 39:10.482
- * THE VERY THOUGHT OF YOU
MAKES MY HEART SING *

39:10.516 --> 39:13.419
* LIKE AN APRIL BREEZE

39:13.452 --> 39:18.790
* ON THE WINGS OF SPRING

39:18.824 --> 39:25.531
- * AND YOU APPEAR
IN ALL YOUR SPLENDOR *

39:26.498 --> 39:31.603
* MY ONE AND ONLY LOVE

39:37.543 --> 39:44.816
YOU KNOW, I ALWAYS DREAMED
ABOUT...

39:44.850 --> 39:49.821
GIVING AWAY MY DAUGHTER
AT HER WEDDING.

39:51.122 --> 39:54.092
- THAT'S VERY SWEET.

39:54.125 --> 39:56.061
MAYBE IT WILL STILL
HAPPEN.

39:57.563 --> 39:58.964
- NO.

40:04.202 --> 40:05.971
OUR DAUGHTER.

40:09.608 --> 40:14.212
BUT COLIN GETS TO DO THAT
INSTEAD OF ME.

40:14.245 --> 40:15.614
WITH TAYLOR.

40:21.887 --> 40:23.589
[sighs]

40:23.622 --> 40:28.894
OF COURSE, THERE'S STILL
ONE LITTLE PROBLEM.

40:30.862 --> 40:33.064
- WHAT'S THAT?

40:36.067 --> 40:38.504
- [whispers indistinct]

40:38.537 --> 40:42.240
- NO! NO! NO!

40:42.273 --> 40:45.977
NO, NO, NO! NO!

40:46.011 --> 40:47.846
- ANNE! ANNE!

40:47.879 --> 40:48.847
- NO!

40:48.880 --> 40:50.482
- I NEED TO GET IN THERE.
MY WIFE NEEDS ME.

40:50.516 --> 40:51.883
- TAKE IT EASY.
JUST TAKE IT EASY.

40:51.917 --> 40:54.152
- PLEASE, LET ME JUST GO IN.
- TAKE IT EASY, OKAY?

40:54.185 --> 40:56.655
- HE KILLED HER.
HE KILLED HER.

40:56.688 --> 41:00.992
HE KILLED HER.
HE KILLED HER. HE KILLED HER.

41:02.661 --> 41:08.166
- DARLING.
- [crying]

41:08.199 --> 41:10.035
- I JUST DON'T GET IT.

41:10.068 --> 41:11.637
I MEAN, WHY KILL THE GIRL?

41:11.670 --> 41:12.871
IT'S NOT PART OF HIS M.O.

41:12.904 --> 41:15.006
- IN HIS MIND,
HE WANTED ANNE TO HURT

41:15.040 --> 41:16.007
THE SAME WAY HE DID.

41:16.041 --> 41:17.876
- AND HE'S STILL
TORTURING THEM.

41:17.909 --> 41:19.611
HE WON'T TELL US
WHERE TAYLOR'S BODY IS.

41:19.645 --> 41:21.146
- WELL, WE'VE CANVASSED

41:21.179 --> 41:22.881
ALL THE HOTELS AND CAFES
WE KNOW HE HIT.

41:22.914 --> 41:24.182
NOTHING YET.

41:24.215 --> 41:26.885
- NO, HE SAID
THAT TAYLOR'S SPECIAL.

41:26.918 --> 41:29.621
HIS USUAL HOTELS
WERE KIND OF MODEST.

41:29.655 --> 41:30.989
WE'VE BEEN LOOKING
IN THE WRONG NEIGHBORHOOD.

41:31.022 --> 41:32.924
WE'VE GOT TO TRY
THE EAST SIDE.

41:36.061 --> 41:38.564
WHEN IS THE LAST TIME
ANYBODY SAW THE GIRL?

41:38.597 --> 41:40.298
- SHE ORDERED ROOM SERVICE
LAST NIGHT.

41:40.331 --> 41:41.600
WHY?
IS EVERYTHING ALL RIGHT?

41:41.633 --> 41:43.635
- HEY, LOOK,
JUST OPEN THE DOOR.

41:46.337 --> 41:47.906
- SEAN?

41:47.939 --> 41:49.575
- TAYLOR.

41:49.608 --> 41:51.543
- WE'VE GOT THE GIRL.
SHE'S ALIVE.

41:51.577 --> 41:54.212
- WHAT'S GOING ON?
WHERE'S SEAN?

41:58.717 --> 42:02.253
- TAYLOR, SEAN TOLD
YOUR MOTHER AND YOUR FATHER

42:02.287 --> 42:04.690
THAT YOU WERE DEAD.

42:06.324 --> 42:08.560
- YOU'RE LYING.
HE WOULD NEVER DO THAT.

42:08.594 --> 42:10.929
- HONEY, YOU DON'T KNOW
WHO HE IS.

42:10.962 --> 42:12.330
- YES, I DO.

42:12.363 --> 42:15.066
THERE'S A REASON I NEVER FELT
CLOSE TO MY DAD.

42:15.100 --> 42:16.702
IT'S BECAUSE HE'S NOT
MY REAL FATHER.

42:16.735 --> 42:17.969
SEAN IS.

42:18.003 --> 42:19.204
LAST NIGHT, HE FINALLY
TOLD ME THE TRUTH.

42:19.237 --> 42:22.073
- TAYLOR, THAT'S NOT TRUE.
- YES, IT IS!

42:22.107 --> 42:23.642
- PUT YOUR CLOTHES ON.
- GET AWAY FROM ME!

42:23.675 --> 42:25.076
I WANT SEAN!

42:28.313 --> 42:31.049
I WANT MY FATHER!
